cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses deep learning in medical imaging, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The focus on semi-supervised learning (SSL) and self-ensembling also suggests a potential fit for artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Finally, the use of disentangled representations and stochastic latent space could also relate to neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
